markets.title: Will Todd Young vote for a resolution ending the national emergency declared to impose duties on articles imported from Canada?
markets.rules_primary: If Todd Young votes for a resolution ending the national emergency declared to impose duties on articles imported from Canada in the || Chamber | before May 1, 2025, then the market resolves to Yes.
markets.rules_secondary: This underlying for this market includes but is not necessarily limited to SJ Res 37 (https://www.kaine.senate.gov/press-releases/kaine-klobuchar-and-warner-announce-expected-vote-timing-on-their-bill-to-undo-canada-tariffs-that-will-raise-costs).
markets.early_close_condition: This market will close and expire early if the event occurs.
